description: StoryTeller is a random story generator.  You can either ask for a specific genre of story you would like to hear (sci-fi, fantasy, scary, etc.) or StoryTeller will choose a genre for you, just ask!
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask story teller for a scary story
Alexa tell story teller to make up a story
Alexa ask story teller to tell us a sci-fi story
name: Story Teller
shortDescription: StoryTeller can tell lots of different kinds of stories.  What kind of story would you like to hear?
